# Homebrew formula for the Vokra CLI (X-07-T24).
#
# BUILD-FROM-SOURCE (ADR docs/adr/X-07-release-train.md §package-managers):
# the formula downloads the tag source tarball and builds the `vokra` CLI with
# cargo (zero external crates — NFR-DS-02 — so the sandboxed build needs no
# network beyond the tarball). Source-based, so it does NOT depend on the
